SELECT authorised_value,lib FROM authorised_values WHERE category='Bsort2'

elements.expression: CASE substring(ExtractValue(ajra,'//datafield[@tag="100"]/subfield[@code="a"]'),18,1) WHEN 'a'  THEN 'a-Jeunesse (général)' WHEN 'b' THEN 'b-Pré-scolaire' WHEN 'c' THEN 'c-Scolaire' WHEN 'd' THEN 'd-Enfant' WHEN 'e' THEN 'e-Jeune adulte' WHEN 'k' THEN 'k-Adulte haut niveau' WHEN 'm' THEN 'm-Adulte grand public' WHEN 'u' THEN 'u-Inconnu' ELSE '~-Invalide' END

elements.expression: CASE substring(ExtractValue(ajra,'//leader'),7,1)  WHEN 'a' THEN 'Doc textuel'  WHEN 'b' THEN 'Doc textuel manuscrit' WHEN 'c' THEN 'Partition' WHEN 'd' THEN 'Partition manuscrite' WHEN 'e' THEN 'Carte' WHEN 'f' THEN 'Carte manuscrite' WHEN 'g' THEN 'Vidéo' WHEN 'i' THEN 'Doc sonore non musical' WHEN 'j' THEN 'Doc sonore musical' WHEN 'k' THEN 'Image/Dessin' WHEN 'l' THEN 'Ress. électronique' WHEN 'm' THEN 'Multimédia' WHEN 'r' THEN 'Objet en 3D' ELSE 'Non défini' END
elements.viewExpression: CASE substring(ExtractValue(#ajra,'//leader'),7,1)  WHEN 'a' THEN 'Doc textuel'  WHEN 'b' THEN 'Doc textuel manuscrit' WHEN 'c' THEN 'Partition' WHEN 'd' THEN 'Partition manuscrite' WHEN 'e' THEN 'Carte' WHEN 'f' THEN 'Carte manuscrite' WHEN 'g' THEN 'Vidéo' WHEN 'i' THEN 'Doc sonore non musical' WHEN 'j' THEN 'Doc sonore musical' WHEN 'k' THEN 'Image/Dessin' WHEN 'l' THEN 'Ress. électronique' WHEN 'm' THEN 'Multimédia' WHEN 'r' THEN 'Objet en 3D' ELSE 'Non défini' END

elements.expression: CASE WHEN SUBSTRING(ExtractValue(#ajra,'//leader'), 7, 2) IN ('am', 'ac','om')  THEN 'Livre imprimé' WHEN SUBSTRING(ExtractValue(#ajra,'//leader'), 7, 2)='as' THEN 'Revue imprimée' WHEN SUBSTRING(ExtractValue(#ajra,'//leader'), 7, 2) IN('gm','gn','gs') THEN 'DVD' WHEN SUBSTRING(ExtractValue(#ajra,'//leader'), 7, 2)='bm' THEN 'Manuscrit' WHEN SUBSTRING(ExtractValue(#ajra,'//leader'), 7, 2) IN ('jm', 'im' ,'jn') THEN 'CD' WHEN SUBSTRING(ExtractValue(#ajra,'//leader'), 7, 2)='km' THEN 'Image fixe' WHEN SUBSTRING(ExtractValue(#ajra,'//leader'), 7, 2)='em' THEN 'Carte imprimée' WHEN SUBSTRING(ExtractValue(#ajra,'//leader'), 7, 2)='cm' THEN 'Partition imprimée' WHEN SUBSTRING(ExtractValue(#ajra,'//leader'), 7, 2) IN ('mm','ms') THEN 'Doc multimedia multisupport' WHEN SUBSTRING(ExtractValue(#ajra,'//leader'), 7, 2)='lm' THEN 'Doc électronique' ELSE 'Autre doc' END
elements.viewExpression: CASE WHEN SUBSTRING(ExtractValue(#ajra,'//leader'), 7, 2) IN ('am', 'ac','om')  THEN 'Livre imprimé' WHEN SUBSTRING(ExtractValue(#ajra,'//leader'), 7, 2)='as' THEN 'Revue imprimée' WHEN SUBSTRING(ExtractValue(#ajra,'//leader'), 7, 2) IN('gm','gn','gs') THEN 'DVD' WHEN SUBSTRING(ExtractValue(#ajra,'//leader'), 7, 2)='bm' THEN 'Manuscrit' WHEN SUBSTRING(ExtractValue(#ajra,'//leader'), 7, 2) IN ('jm', 'im' ,'jn') THEN 'CD' WHEN SUBSTRING(ExtractValue(#ajra,'//leader'), 7, 2)='km' THEN 'Image fixe' WHEN SUBSTRING(ExtractValue(#ajra,'//leader'), 7, 2)='em' THEN 'Carte imprimée' WHEN SUBSTRING(ExtractValue(#ajra,'//leader'), 7, 2)='cm' THEN 'Partition imprimée' WHEN SUBSTRING(ExtractValue(#ajra,'//leader'), 7, 2) IN ('mm','ms') THEN 'Doc multimedia multisupport' WHEN SUBSTRING(ExtractValue(#ajra,'//leader'), 7, 2)='lm' THEN 'Doc électronique' ELSE 'Autre doc' END
